      <title>Tic Tac Toe - Classic Two-Player Game</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/24/Tic%20Tac%20Toe/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/24/Tic%20Tac%20Toe/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="About-the-Game"><a href="#About-the-Game" class="headerlink" title="About the Game"></a>About the Game</h2><p>The classic Tic Tac Toe game you can play in your browser.<br>Challenge a friend or play against the computer AI.</p><h2 id="How-to-Play"><a href="#How-to-Play" class="headerlink" title="How to Play"></a>How to Play</h2><ul><li>Click on a cell to place your mark (X or O)</li><li>Get three in a row to win</li><li>Play against AI or a friend</li></ul><h2 id="Play-Online"><a href="#Play-Online" class="headerlink" title="Play Online"></a>Play Online</h2><p><a href="https://tictactoegame.com/">Play Tic Tac Toe</a></p><h2 id="Open-Source-Info"><a href="#Open-Source-Info" class="headerlink" title="Open Source Info"></a>Open Source Info</h2><ul><li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/tannerlinsley/react-tictactoe">https://github.com/tannerlinsley/react-tictactoe</a></li><li>License: MIT</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
