      <title>Flappy Bird - Simple Casual Game</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/24/Flappy%20Bird/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/24/Flappy%20Bird/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="About-the-Game"><a href="#About-the-Game" class="headerlink" title="About the Game"></a>About the Game</h2><p>A simple and addictive Flappy Bird clone, built for the browser.<br>Tap or click to flap your wings and avoid the pipes.</p><h2 id="How-to-Play"><a href="#How-to-Play" class="headerlink" title="How to Play"></a>How to Play</h2><ul><li>Desktop: Click or press any key to flap</li><li>Mobile: Tap the screen</li><li>Avoid hitting the pipes or the ground</li></ul><h2 id="Play-Online"><a href="#Play-Online" class="headerlink" title="Play Online"></a>Play Online</h2><p><a href="https://flappybird.io/">Play Flappy Bird</a></p><h2 id="Open-Source-Info"><a href="#Open-Source-Info" class="headerlink" title="Open Source Info"></a>Open Source Info</h2><ul><li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/nebez/floppybird">https://github.com/nebez/floppybird</a></li><li>License: MIT</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
