      <title>Breakout - Classic Brick Breaker</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/24/Breakout/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/24/Breakout/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="About-the-Game"><a href="#About-the-Game" class="headerlink" title="About the Game"></a>About the Game</h2><p>A modern browser remake of the classic Breakout arcade game.<br>Use your paddle to bounce the ball and break all the bricks to clear the level.</p><h2 id="How-to-Play"><a href="#How-to-Play" class="headerlink" title="How to Play"></a>How to Play</h2><ul><li>Desktop: Left&#x2F;Right arrows to move paddle</li><li>Mobile: Swipe left&#x2F;right</li><li>Clear all bricks to win</li></ul><h2 id="Play-Online"><a href="#Play-Online" class="headerlink" title="Play Online"></a>Play Online</h2><p><a href="https://breakoutgame.io/">Play Breakout</a></p><h2 id="Open-Source-Info"><a href="#Open-Source-Info" class="headerlink" title="Open Source Info"></a>Open Source Info</h2><ul><li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/lexcast/Breakout">https://github.com/lexcast/Breakout</a></li><li>License: MIT</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
