      <title>Minesweeper - Classic Puzzle</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/24/Minesweeper/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/24/Minesweeper/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="About-the-Game"><a href="#About-the-Game" class="headerlink" title="About the Game"></a>About the Game</h2><p>The classic Minesweeper puzzle game, now playable in your browser.<br>Uncover tiles, avoid mines, and mark them with flags to clear the board.</p><h2 id="How-to-Play"><a href="#How-to-Play" class="headerlink" title="How to Play"></a>How to Play</h2><ul><li>Left click: Reveal a tile</li><li>Right click: Flag a suspected mine</li><li>Win by clearing all non-mine tiles</li></ul><h2 id="Play-Online"><a href="#Play-Online" class="headerlink" title="Play Online"></a>Play Online</h2><p><a href="https://minesweeper.online/">Play Minesweeper</a></p><h2 id="Open-Source-Info"><a href="#Open-Source-Info" class="headerlink" title="Open Source Info"></a>Open Source Info</h2><ul><li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/featherbear/minesweeper">https://github.com/featherbear/minesweeper</a></li><li>License: MIT</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
